Option 1: Test Mode (Console Only)
bash
pip install python-dotenv
python weather_buddy_email.py
This will show you the notification in console without actually sending email.

Option 2: Send Actual Emails
To send real emails to xxx.com:

Enable 2-Factor Authentication on your Gmail account

Generate an App Password:

Go to: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords

Select "Mail" and your device

Copy the 16-character password

Create .env file:

text
SENDER_EMAIL=xxx
SENDER_APP_PASSWORD=your_16_char_app_password
Run the script:

bash
python weather_buddy_email.py
